					<p class="txt">
						A good well provides a stable supply of clear, clean water<br />
						To the places and people in need of it.<br /><br />
						
						For a well to work as it should, it cannot be dug halfheartedly.<br />
						It must be worked patiently, with dedication –<br />
						Yet even when water is struck, work is far from over.<br /><br />

						To prevent water from the well being sullied,<br />
						To avoid its structure being compromised by the elements,<br />
						The skills of the sincere must be gathered.<br /><br />

						Only then – established and its contents pure –<br />
						Can the well provide a haven at which to gather.<br /><br />

						To drink up each other’s stories just as the water itself,<br /> 
						For connections to flow just as the water itself.<br /><br />

						Hydrated, inspired, those at the well discover new dreams,<br />
						Realize old hopes, plan healthy endeavors –<br />
						Even, perhaps, another well.<br /><br />
						
						The Wells Investment is a company of people that make wells –<br />
						And we do it well.<br /><br />
						
						We pay the price of sweat and studiousness to find clear water;<br />
						We manage our wells with unparalleled technical attention;<br />
						We nurture the ecosystems that form around what we craft;<br />
						All so our wells bring life, grow healthily, and spark more wells.<br /><br />
						
						<span class="main-c">
							Through honesty, dedication and creativity,<br />
							We craft wells that run deep with human vitality.<br />					
							This is the purpose, philosophy and method of The Wells Investment.
						</span>
